releaseNotes:
1.3.6  2023-06-25 - chatty radars excessive debug logging bug fix
1.3.5 2023-05-28 - fixes for _TZE200_lu01t0zl TS0601_RADAR_MIR-TY-FALL mmWave radar (only the basic Motion and radarSensitivity is supported for now).
1.3.4  2023-05-19 - added _TZE204_sxm7l9xa mmWave radar to TS0601_YXZBRB58_RADAR group; isRadar() bug fix;
1.3.3  2023-05-14 - code cleanup; added TS0202 _TZ3210_cwamkvua [Motion Sensor and Scene Switch]; added _TZE204_sooucan5 radar in a new TS0601_YXZBRB58_RADAR group (for tests); added reportingTime4in1 to setPar command options;
1.3.2  2023-04-17  - 4-in-1 parameter for adjusting the reporting time; supressed debug logs when ignoreDistance is flipped on; 'Send Event when parameters change' parameter is removed (events are always sent when there is a change); fadingTime and detectionDelay change was not logged and not sent as an event;
1.3.1  2023-03-29 - added 'invertMotion' option; 4in1 (Fantem) Refresh Tuya Magic; invertMotion is set to true by default for _TZE200_3towulqd;
1.3.0  2023-03-22  -'_TYST11_7hfcudw5' moved to 3-in-1 group; added deviceProfiles; fixed initializaiton missing on the first pairing; added batteryVoltage; added tuyaVersion; added delayed battery event; removed state.lastBattery; caught sensitivity par exception; fixed forcedProfile was not set automatically on Initialize; 
1.2.2 2023-03-18 - typo in a log transaction fixed; added TS0202 _TZ3000_kmh5qpmb as a 3-in-1 type device; added _TZE200_xpq2rzhq radar; bug fix in setMotion()
1.2.1  2023-02-10 - reverted the unsuccessful changes made in the latest 1.2.0 version for _TZE200_3towulqd (2in1); added _TZE200_v6ossqfy as BlackSquareRadar; removed the wrongly added TUYATEC T/H sensor...
1.2.0  2023-02-07 - healthStatus; supressed repetative Radar detection delay and Radar fading time Info messages in the logs; logsOff missed when hub is restarted bug fix; capability 'Health Check'; _TZE200_3towulqd (2in1) new firmware versions fix for motion; 
1.1.1 2023-01-08 - illuminance event bug fix; fadingTime minimum value 0.5; SetPar command shows in the UI the list of all possible parameters; _TZ3000_6ygjfyll bug fix;
1.1.0  2022-12-25 - SetPar() command;  added 'Send Event when parameters change' option; code cleanup; added _TZE200_holel4dk; added 4-in-1 _TZ3210_rxqls8v0, _TZ3210_wuhzzfqg
1.0.16 2022-12-10 - _TZE200_3towulqd (2-in-1) motion detection inverted; excluded from IAS group;
1.0.15 2022-12-03 - OWON 0x0406 cluster binding; added _TZE204_ztc6ggyl _TZE200_ar0slwnd _TZE200_sfiy5tfs _TZE200_mrf6vtua (was wrongly 3in1) mmWave radards;
1.0.14 2022-10-31 - added Bond motion sensor ZX-BS-J11W
1.0.13 2022-09-25 - added _TZE200_jva8ink8 AUBESS radar; 2-in-1 Sensitivity setting bug fix
1.0.12 2022-09-22 - added _TZE200_wukb7rhc MOES radar
1.0.11 2022-08-22 - IAS devices initialization improvements; presence threshold increased to 4 hours; 3in1 exceptions bug fixes; 3in1 and 4in1 exceptions bug fixes;
1.0.10 2022-08-15 - added Lux threshold parameter; square black radar LED configuration is resent back when device is powered on; round black PIR sensor powerSource is set to DC; added OWON OCP305 Presence Sensor
1.0.9 2022-08-11 - degrees Celsius symbol bug fix; added square black radar _TZE200_0u3bj3rc support, temperatureOffset bug fix; decimal/number type prferences bug fix
